text: You seem to be in a good mood, Chiyuki.

Walking through a new town
makes me feel excited, you know?

Oh, I understand that feeling.
Even small sights seem fresh.

Discovering small differences,
or even finding the same places...

Everywhere I look, it's enjoyable...
I can't help but look around.
